snippet.title: Dragon Audit | Announcement Trailer | PS4
snippet.description:
A battle accountant storms the castle to rescue a princess, but accidentally rescues an overly friendly dragoness instead.

Dragon Audit is a humorous adventure story in the vein of point & click classics, told with an anime-inspired 3D visual style and modern controller-friendly input. Coming soon to PlayStation 4.
